14:09.744 --> 14:11.745
Terrific.

14:12.746 --> 14:13.646
So, how's he doing?

14:13.647 --> 14:15.715
Who?
Alan.

14:15.716 --> 14:17.184
Oh, oh, Charlie.

14:17.185 --> 14:19.218
Uh, uh, he's doing fine--
just fine.

14:19.219 --> 14:21.854
Good, good.

14:21.855 --> 14:24.825
In fact, he told me to
tell you happy birthday.

14:24.826 --> 14:26.926
