Tell him I said thanks.

14:26.927 --> 14:28.361
I will.

14:28.362 --> 14:30.529
And I'm sure he'd say,
"You're welcome."

14:34.267 --> 14:36.501
So, um, how are
you doing?

14:36.502 --> 14:38.436
