not Charlie.

14:38.437 --> 14:39.870
Although I'm sure he'd
be interested.

14:39.871 --> 14:42.005
Not that I'd tell him,
unless you want me to.

14:42.006 --> 14:43.339
Do you want me to? Wait.

14:43.340 --> 14:45.774
Tell me how you're doing first,
and then we can decide.

14:47.010 --> 14:48.710
I'm doing fine, Alan.

14:48.711 --> 14:50.812
Good, good. Oh, so is Charlie.

14:51.680 --> 14:53.047
Can we change the subject?

14:53.048 --> 14:55.783
You're the one
who brought it up, but sure.

15:00.321 --> 15:03.589
You ever think about your
dad and Ed having sex?

15:05.892 --> 15:08.160
"Happy birthday,
thinking of you."

15:09.495 --> 15:11.095
What's wrong with it?

15:11.096 --> 15:13.664
It's, what to you call it,
redumbnent.

15:13.665 --> 15:16.066
Redumbnent?

15:16.067 --> 15:19.936
Yeah. You got her a present
and you got her a birthday card.

15:19.937 --> 15:21.571
You're obviously
thinking of her.

15:21.572 --> 15:24.407
So <i>saying</i> you're thinking
of her is redumbnent.

15:24.408 --> 15:26.308
So if you act like a moron,

15:26.309 --> 15:29.578
