15:35.350 --> 15:37.351
Wait here.
I'll be right back.

15:37.352 --> 15:39.086
Why can't I
go with you?

15:39.087 --> 15:41.821
Because I'm just
gonna give Chelsea
the bracelet and leave.

15:41.822 --> 15:43.723
